00:21:59,880 --> 00:22:00,770
It's okay.

306
00:22:01,640 --> 00:22:03,770
Last night, I just wanted

307
00:22:04,360 --> 00:22:05,930
to say happy birthday to you.

308
00:22:06,840 --> 00:22:08,880
It was your 18th birthday,

309
00:22:08,880 --> 00:22:10,930
