316
00:22:24,320 --> 00:22:26,050
You should go. It's okay.

317
00:22:26,120 --> 00:22:26,960
Uncomfortable?

318
00:22:27,730 --> 00:22:28,570
You...

319
00:22:50,840 --> 00:22:51,680
Lin Ge.

320
00:22:52,730 --> 00:22:53,770
Happy birthday.

321
00:22:54,560 --> 00:22:55,730
Wish you happiness every day.

322
00:22:56,600 --> 00:22:58,050
It's your birthday.

323
00:22:58,840 --> 00:23:00,250
I'd like to take this opportunity

324
00:23:00,530 --> 00:23:01,840
to express my feelings.

325
00:23:02,690 --> 00:23:04,560
We went to the sports school,

326
00:23:05,490 --> 00:23:06,560
the provincial team,

327
00:23:07,320 --> 00:23:08,690
and the national team together.

328
00:23:09,390 --> 00:23:10,770
I gradually realized

329
00:23:11,020 --> 00:23:12,860
my life was full of sunshine.

330
00:23:13,480 --> 00:23:15,290
We grew up and hung out together

331
00:23:16,010 --> 00:23:18,530
every day like brothers.

332
00:23:19,120 --> 00:23:20,730
We had so much to talk about.

333
00:23:21,880 --> 00:23:23,530
However, I didn't realize

334
00:23:24,770 --> 00:23:26,210
you'd been

335
00:23:27,160 --> 00:23:29,120
important and irreplaceable

336
00:23:29,770 --> 00:23:31,120
in my heart.

337
00:23:32,080 --> 00:23:33,120
Not until now

338
00:23:34,160 --> 00:23:35,080
have I realized

339
00:23:35,080 --> 00:23:37,600
the reason I want to see you every day

340
00:23:38,560 --> 00:23:39,930
is because I like you.

341
00:23:40,770 --> 00:23:41,880
Therefore, Lin Ge,

342
00:23:42,320 --> 00:23:44,840
I've finally made up my mind to tell you

343
00:23:45,290 --> 00:23:46,360
I like you.

344
00:23:46,770 --> 00:23:48,450
I've liked you for a long time,

345
00:23:48,880 --> 00:23:50,080
and I won't stop.

346
00:23:50,840 --> 00:23:52,050
Please be my girlfriend.

347
00:24:09,840 --> 00:24:11,120
The same group of people, right?

348
00:24:11,450 --> 00:24:12,290
Before and after

349
00:24:12,290 --> 00:24:13,250
the Winter Olympics?

350
00:24:14,160 --> 00:24:15,000
Got it.

351
00:24:15,690 --> 00:24:17,210
