Same as usual,

362
00:24:43,930 --> 00:24:45,360
just some boring questions.

363
00:24:45,970 --> 00:24:47,730
It might affect
Xie Lingwei and your training.

364
00:24:47,930 --> 00:24:48,880
Mr. Li

365
00:24:49,640 --> 00:24:51,260
is about to lose his temper.

366
00:24:51,930 --> 00:24:52,840
I heard

367
00:24:52,840 --> 00:24:54,210
he argued with our manager.

368
00:24:54,530 --> 00:24:55,370
We have to

369
00:24:55,690 --> 00:24:57,500
cooperate with the publicity.

370
00:25:01,360 --> 00:25:02,200
Never mind.

371
00:25:04,800 --> 00:25:05,640
What's wrong?

372
00:25:06,010 --> 00:25:06,850
Nothing.

373
00:25:06,850 --> 00:25:08,560
