to the girls' dorm this late.

374
00:25:08,800 --> 00:25:09,730
I'll tell them on WeChat.

375
00:25:11,080 --> 00:25:12,490
When did you become so mature?

376
00:25:12,490 --> 00:25:13,730
(Select Contact)

377
00:25:13,730 --> 00:25:16,530
Last time, I knocked on
Chao Jinting's door at 10:30 p.m.,

378
00:25:16,770 --> 00:25:18,020
