379
00:25:18,020 --> 00:25:18,860
(Send)

380
00:25:19,080 --> 00:25:20,210
You deserved it.

381
00:25:26,020 --> 00:25:27,060
(Group Chat)
Gosh.

382
00:25:27,530 --> 00:25:29,530
So dramatic. What's wrong?

383
00:25:30,600 --> 00:25:32,730
Nothing. I made a mistake.

384
00:25:34,860 --> 00:25:37,060
(Here's the filming notice.
I created a group by accident.)

385
00:25:37,060 --> 00:25:39,900
(Leave the group after reading it,
