386
00:25:54,160 --> 00:25:56,640
Gao Kai is so stupid.

387
00:25:57,400 --> 00:25:58,690
Jinting, it's not a big deal.

388
00:25:59,010 --> 00:26:00,970
I didn't know a mass message
would create a group.

389
00:26:01,180 --> 00:26:02,640
It's obvious that he didn't want

390
00:26:02,640 --> 00:26:04,080
Chen Mingyuan to see it.

391
00:26:04,530 --> 00:26:06,050
He was too lazy to send it to everyone

392
00:26:06,210 --> 00:26:07,700
and accidentally created a group.

393
00:26:08,360 --> 00:26:09,490
Look what he's done.

394
00:26:09,730 --> 00:26:12,530
