396
00:26:15,780 --> 00:26:17,400
Did he leave the group

397
00:26:17,400 --> 00:26:18,800
after reading it?

398
00:26:18,900 --> 00:26:20,120
Nie Chi isn't there either.

399
00:26:20,560 --> 00:26:22,810
I screenshot it immediately.

400
00:26:24,420 --> 00:26:25,290
Jinting,

401
00:26:25,290 --> 00:26:27,050
you're really a gossip expert.

402
00:26:27,800 --> 00:26:29,130
So, what's going on

403
00:26:29,130 --> 00:26:30,210
with Chen Mingyuan?

404
00:26:30,370 --> 00:26:31,690
Why did Gao Kai set him up?

405
00:26:32,560 --> 00:26:34,210
Set up? Who was set up?

406
00:26:34,560 --> 00:26:36,080
What are you talking about?

407
00:26:36,410 --> 00:26:37,250
What is it?

408
00:26:37,970 --> 00:26:41,320
Well, this is a very long story.

409
00:26:42,560 --> 00:26:44,640
Once upon a time,

410
00:26:44,930 --> 00:26:47,690
Chen Mingyuan and Yu Siyang got together

411
00:26:48,120 --> 00:26:50,360
in the provincial team

412
00:26:50,530 --> 00:26:52,800
and joined the national team together.

413
00:26:53,490 --> 00:26:55,880
They were an enviable

414
00:26:55,880 --> 00:26:57,530
perfect couple.

415
00:26:59,360 --> 00:27:00,840
And then? Go on.

416
00:27:01,160 --> 00:27:04,600
But the relationship
affected their performances.

417
00:27:05,120 --> 00:27:07,080
Chen Mingyuan was 17 or 18 years old,

418
00:27:07,360 --> 00:27:08,200
very talented.

419
00:27:08,290 --> 00:27:09,250
Mr. Li wanted him

420
00:27:09,250 --> 00:27:10,880
to lead long-distance events,

421
00:27:11,360 --> 00:27:13,400
whereas Siyang wasn't that lucky.

422
00:27:13,730 --> 00:27:15,600
There were many talented female skaters.

423
00:27:16,010 --> 00:27:17,010
Mr. Li split them up.

424
00:27:18,600 --> 00:27:19,880
What happened?

425
00:27:20,490 --> 00:27:22,320
Chen Mingyuan stayed in the team,

426
00:27:22,600 --> 00:27:24,320
and Siyang had two options,

427
00:27:24,400 --> 00:27:25,560
college

428
00:27:25,560 --> 00:27:26,530
or provincial team,

429
00:27:26,530 --> 00:27:27,840
and she went to college.

430
00:27:28,730 --> 00:27:31,640
Didn't they resist?

431
00:27:32,530 --> 00:27:33,560
How?

432
00:27:34,120 --> 00:27:35,400
They weren't Romeo and Juliet,

433
00:27:36,050 --> 00:27:37,640
and Mr. Li was the king.

434
00:27:38,210 --> 00:27:40,400
Besides, if they retired together,

435
00:27:40,730 --> 00:27:42,770
would over ten years of practice
be worth it?

436
00:27:43,690 --> 00:27:45,560
They'd both been trained
for over ten years.

437
00:27:45,840 --> 00:27:47,530
Why did it have to be Siyang?

438
00:27:47,770 --> 00:27:48,610
Exactly.

439
00:27:49,880 --> 00:27:53,210
Speaking of which,
here's the cruelest part.

440
00:27:54,250 --> 00:27:56,450
When Siyang left,

441
00:27:56,450 --> 00:27:59,930
she said in front of everyone,

442
00:28:00,490 --> 00:28:04,050
"You're carrying on our dream.

443
00:28:04,530 --> 00:28:06,160
If you can't win the Olympic Games,

444
00:28:06,600 --> 00:28:08,690
my departure will be meaningless."

445
00:28:09,770 --> 00:28:11,010
Oh my god.

446
00:28:11,930 --> 00:28:13,490
Olympic champion.

447
00:28:14,120 --> 00:28:16,450
That was such a high goal.

448
00:28:17,690 --> 00:28:18,880
It's said

449
00:28:19,050 --> 00:28:20,560
he had the chance

450
00:28:20,560 --> 00:28:22,360
to make it before 21 years old,

451
00:28:22,840 --> 00:28:25,080
but he was so unlucky

452
00:28:25,320 --> 00:28:27,400
that he got injured
before two Olympic Games.

453
00:28:27,560 --> 00:28:29,290
He came here at the age of 17

454
00:28:29,450 --> 00:28:31,400
but didn't go to the Winter Olympics
until he's 26.

455
00:28:32,690 --> 00:28:34,600
It's not his best days anymore.

456
00:28:35,970 --> 00:28:37,450
They were both professional athletes.

457
00:28:37,770 --> 00:28:38,930
Why would the relationship

458
00:28:38,930 --> 00:28:40,600
affect their training?

459
00:28:41,640 --> 00:28:44,120
Love makes people

460
00:28:44,120 --> 00:28:45,490
blind and emotional.

461
00:28:46,080 --> 00:28:48,930
At their age, anyone would want
passionate love.

462
00:28:49,600 --> 00:28:51,530
If Mr. Li waited for them for two years,

463
00:28:51,530 --> 00:28:52,640
maybe they'd be stable.

464
00:28:53,490 --> 00:28:55,290
There are a lot of talents.

465
00:28:55,290 --> 00:28:56,360
No one will wait for you.

466
00:28:56,530 --> 00:28:57,930
If you fail, you'll leave.

467
00:28:58,360 --> 00:29:00,250
However, Mr. Li is not always cruel.

468
00:29:00,530 --> 00:29:02,120
When you're good again,

469
00:29:02,120 --> 00:29:03,290
he'll invite you back.

470
00:29:05,120 --> 00:29:06,250
So,

471
00:29:06,630 --> 00:29:09,110
Gao Kai doesn't want
Chen Mingyuan to find out

472
00:29:09,320 --> 00:29:11,840
Siyang is coming tomorrow.

473
00:29:12,010 --> 00:29:12,880
Yes.

474
00:29:13,160 --> 00:29:15,360
He ran away last time, didn't he?

475
00:29:18,210 --> 00:29:20,250
There'll be a great show tomorrow.

476
00:29:24,210 --> 00:29:25,120
Okay, enough.

477
00:29:25,710 --> 00:29:27,360
Gossip time is over. Go to sleep.

478
00:29:28,400 --> 00:29:30,450
Let's wait and see.

479
00:29:30,880 --> 00:29:32,290
Bye, Jinting.

480
00:29:34,970 --> 00:29:35,840
As the team leader,

481
00:29:35,840 --> 00:29:37,120
do you think it's stressful

482
00:29:37,120 --> 00:29:38,640
to unite old and new teammates?

483
00:29:38,840 --> 00:29:39,880
It's definitely stressful.

484
00:29:40,360 --> 00:29:41,840
However, we're a team.

485
00:29:41,970 --> 00:29:43,290
It's the old athletes' duty

486
00:29:43,360 --> 00:29:45,160
to help and guide the newcomers.

487
00:29:45,400 --> 00:29:46,970
Only when the team is stronger

488
00:29:47,050 --> 00:29:48,800
can everyone make bigger progress.

489
00:29:49,600 --> 00:29:50,640
Siyang

490
00:29:50,730 --> 00:29:53,880
said in front of everyone,

491
00:29:54,210 --> 00:29:55,970
"If you can't win the Olympic Games,

492
00:29:56,220 --> 00:29:57,960
my departure will be meaningless."

493
00:29:57,960 --> 00:29:58,880
As we know,

494
00:29:58,880 --> 00:30:01,780
we're very likely to win gold medals
in short track speed skating.

495
00:30:02,130 --> 00:30:03,320
To secure our success...

496
00:30:03,320 --> 00:30:04,690
I'm looking at Siyang.

497
00:30:04,690 --> 00:30:06,160
Stop sighing.

498
00:30:06,560 --> 00:30:07,880
Well, don't worry about it.

499
00:30:07,880 --> 00:30:09,970
I was telling you not to overthink it.

500
00:30:10,140 --> 00:30:11,450
Apart from Mr. Li's assignments...

501
00:30:11,450 --> 00:30:12,690
I'm wondering what kind of

502
00:30:12,880 --> 00:30:14,450
videos they'll make based on

503
00:30:14,450 --> 00:30:15,800
the interview of Xie Lingwei and me.

504
00:30:16,130 --> 00:30:17,080
As for preventive measures...

505
00:30:17,080 --> 00:30:18,840
If they want a hot topic,

506
00:30:18,970 --> 00:30:19,860
they'll try their best

507
00:30:19,870 --> 00:30:21,770
