508
00:30:22,200 --> 00:30:24,390
- We'll do our best.
- Why didn't they make videos of us?

509
00:30:24,970 --> 00:30:25,840
I believe in you.

510
00:30:26,210 --> 00:30:27,690
So, this is the end

511
00:30:27,690 --> 00:30:29,120
of the interview.

512
00:30:29,600 --> 00:30:30,440
Okay. Thanks.

513
00:30:30,730 --> 00:30:31,570
Do your best.

514
00:30:36,800 --> 00:30:38,730
Siyang, who else do you want to talk to?

515
00:30:38,970 --> 00:30:41,050
I remember Xie Lingwei
did well last time,

516
00:30:41,050 --> 00:30:42,080
but she was nervous.

517
00:30:42,450 --> 00:30:44,010
I want to talk to her.

518
00:30:44,410 --> 00:30:45,250
Xie Lingwei.

519
00:30:45,990 --> 00:30:46,830
Xie Lingwei.

520
00:30:48,250 --> 00:30:49,560
Xie Lingwei!

521
00:30:53,010 --> 00:30:53,880
She's young.

522
00:30:54,290 --> 00:30:55,160
She's cute.

523
00:30:56,970 --> 00:30:58,220
- Hi.
- Hi.

524
00:30:59,080 --> 00:30:59,920
Well, Mr. Li,

525
00:31:00,360 --> 00:31:02,600
