526
00:31:02,840 --> 00:31:04,450
I remember that boy did well.

527
00:31:04,590 --> 00:31:06,240
Nie Chi, right? Nie...

528
00:31:08,010 --> 00:31:09,160
Brat.

529
00:31:10,770 --> 00:31:13,360
Coach, can Lin Ge come?

530
00:31:13,360 --> 00:31:14,450
They're roommates

531
00:31:14,450 --> 00:31:15,400
