541
00:31:30,290 --> 00:31:32,520
Because you're pretty.

542
00:31:32,690 --> 00:31:33,930
Sweet girl.

543
00:31:34,080 --> 00:31:35,530
Go ahead. I have work to do.

544
00:31:35,530 --> 00:31:36,370
Okay.

545
00:31:36,690 --> 00:31:37,730
Sit down. Don't be nervous.

546
00:31:37,730 --> 00:31:38,570
Okay.

547
00:31:43,290 --> 00:31:45,360
Wei, you were nervous last time.

548
00:31:45,600 --> 00:31:47,160
Your roommate

549
00:31:47,280 --> 00:31:48,720
is here by your side.

550
00:31:48,890 --> 00:31:49,970
Are you feeling better?

551
00:31:51,250 --> 00:31:52,640
Well, Lin Ge, let's start with you.

552
00:31:52,880 --> 00:31:53,840
How have you been

553
00:31:53,840 --> 00:31:54,930
