554
00:31:56,840 --> 00:31:57,770
To be honest,

555
00:31:57,770 --> 00:31:59,320
many things have happened.

556
00:31:59,320 --> 00:32:01,600
It's stressful to serve
the national team.

557
00:32:02,120 --> 00:32:04,770
Luckily, we're like a family.

558
00:32:10,530 --> 00:32:11,370
Go!

559
00:32:12,320 --> 00:32:13,290
Okay, I got it.

560
00:32:13,290 --> 00:32:14,130
I can walk.

561
00:32:15,050 --> 00:32:15,890
Don't run.

562
00:32:16,450 --> 00:32:17,770
