00:32:35,690 --> 00:32:37,970
Siyang gave up
short track speed skating.

570
00:32:37,970 --> 00:32:39,160
That's such a pity.

571
00:32:39,390 --> 00:32:40,250
Their relationship

572
00:32:40,250 --> 00:32:42,120
destroyed her athletic career.

573
00:32:42,490 --> 00:32:43,330
That was cruel.

574
00:32:43,800 --> 00:32:44,800
It's not Mr. Li's fault.

575
00:32:45,160 --> 00:32:46,400
We need self-control,

576
00:32:47,400 --> 00:32:48,240
understand?

577
00:32:50,560 --> 00:32:52,360
I... I didn't see you

578
00:32:52,360 --> 00:32:53,490
last time.

579
00:32:53,690 --> 00:32:55,120
I thought you wouldn't come.

580
00:32:57,560 --> 00:32:59,930
What... do you want to say?

581
00:33:00,360 --> 00:33:01,560
I want to say

582
00:33:03,730 --> 00:33:04,570
I'm sorry.

583
00:33:04,970 --> 00:33:05,970
It's been eight years.

584
00:33:07,290 --> 00:33:09,400
Sorry, I couldn't fulfill the promise.

585
00:33:10,930 --> 00:33:13,530
So, I want to...

586
00:33:13,600 --> 00:33:15,800
You... don't have to apologize.

587
00:33:16,160 --> 00:33:17,690
I know it hasn't been easy for you

588
00:33:17,770 --> 00:33:19,320
over the past eight years

589
00:33:20,010 --> 00:33:22,120
because I used to be an athlete too.

590
00:33:23,210 --> 00:33:25,560
Mingyuan, I only hope

591
00:33:26,050 --> 00:33:28,120
you can seize this opportunity.

592
00:33:29,320 --> 00:33:31,840
Keep fighting. Don't give up.

593
00:33:34,640 --> 00:33:36,560
I won't miss my last chance.

594
00:33:47,840 --> 00:33:50,050
(National Ice Sports Base)
(Dating under Mr. Li's nose)

595
00:33:50,050 --> 00:33:51,640
(is a dead end,)

596
00:33:51,930 --> 00:33:54,450
