602
00:34:06,560 --> 00:34:08,240
Why would I?

603
00:34:10,680 --> 00:34:11,970
You've been on the floor

604
00:34:11,970 --> 00:34:13,080
all night.

605
00:34:14,120 --> 00:34:15,970
I wanted to exercise,

606
00:34:16,280 --> 00:34:18,490
but I had so many thoughts

607
00:34:18,800 --> 00:34:20,400
