617
00:34:54,930 --> 00:34:56,760
Here. I bought all kinds of bread.

618
00:34:56,760 --> 00:34:57,850
Here's milk.

619
00:34:58,640 --> 00:34:59,560
And this.

620
00:35:00,050 --> 00:35:01,490
Well, I...

621
00:35:01,490 --> 00:35:03,160
You also have to eat. Bye.

622
00:35:03,160 --> 00:35:04,280
Don't forget to eat it.

623
00:35:10,050 --> 00:35:11,530
Fang Chao, what are you doing?

624
00:35:12,970 --> 00:35:14,120
You're drinking water, right?

625
00:35:14,600 --> 00:35:15,440
Lin Ge.

626
00:35:24,010 --> 00:35:24,850
Nie Chi's here.

627
00:35:25,160 --> 00:35:26,720
