629
00:35:31,530 --> 00:35:32,410
No.

630
00:35:32,640 --> 00:35:34,160
How's your training?

631
00:35:35,640 --> 00:35:37,970
It's... good. How about you?

632
00:35:38,200 --> 00:35:39,720
We're good.

633
00:35:44,930 --> 00:35:45,850
We?

634
00:35:46,760 --> 00:35:48,080
You're good?

635
00:35:48,850 --> 00:35:49,970
Stop kidding.

636
00:35:50,240 --> 00:35:51,240
