640
00:36:06,450 --> 00:36:07,640
I'm also doing well in training.

641
00:36:13,010 --> 00:36:13,850
Good.

642
00:36:37,200 --> 00:36:38,040
Okay.

643
00:36:39,850 --> 00:36:41,760
Lin Ge, what's wrong?

644
00:36:42,530 --> 00:36:44,050
Starting reaction is your strength.

645
00:36:44,280 --> 00:36:45,120
You lost it.

646
00:36:47,890 --> 00:36:49,330
Mr. Li, give me another chance.

647
00:36:50,890 --> 00:36:51,890
You're distracted.

648
00:36:51,930 --> 00:36:53,010
Adjust yourself.

649
00:37:08,160 --> 00:37:09,490
Why are you shaking?

650
00:37:10,050 --> 00:37:11,120
Are you injured?

651
00:37:11,600 --> 00:37:12,440
No.

652
00:37:12,850 --> 00:37:14,080
What's on your mind?

653
00:37:14,680 --> 00:37:15,520
Hold still.

654
00:37:22,410 --> 00:37:23,250
You too!

655
00:37:23,600 --> 00:37:24,490
Concentration!

656
00:37:24,490 --> 00:37:25,640
What's wrong with you guys?

657
00:37:28,640 --> 00:37:29,480
You two,

658
00:37:29,720 --> 00:37:31,410
